Create a Service Account named deploy-user in admin-ns namespace. Also create a Role and RoleBinding named deploy-user-role and deploy-user-role-binding where role is able to
- Create, Update, view and Delete Pods resources
- Create, Update, view and Delete Deployment resources
- Create, view and Delete CronJobs resources

Also check whether the user is able to perform such activities without creating contexts and write command in /opt/rbac/rbac-sa-check.sh

Finally, Create respective token for the ServiceAccount and create context named deploy-user-context for the current kubernetes cluster. Use the context and create a deployment with 3 replicas with image httpd.